column1: Directions: Pick an unindexed section with similar file names on the spreadsheet, open the file listed under File Name in the folder here, extract as much information as you can and place them in this sheet.  Use the information in the file as primary information.  Use information from file name and surrounding files as secondary information.  For the sake of consistency, use dropdown or make sure data validation errors are cleared.  (Note that if you start typing, google sheets should auto-complete.) For state/national files, leave Comp Month as -.  If there is something that doesn't fit a dropdown/data validation, leave a comment describing the issue.
